    "Statistical analysis was performed using Statistical Package for Social Sciences (SPSS) for Windows, Version 25.0.",
    "achieved 100% concordance, five had reported use of the CONSORT-AI checklist and one had not.",
    "Median concordance varied between geographical regions: China (79%, IQR 71-85%), USA (86%, IQR 73-91%), Japan (86%, IQR 82-96%) and Europe (93%, IQR 86-93%).",
    "*Concordance defined as proportion of \"Yes\" or \"N/A\" responses across all studies, rounded to nearest whole number.",
    "Nature Communications | (2024)15:1619"
